## Workflow / process rules for mobile work

### 10. One actionable step at a time
- one step at a time unless no feedback is needed

### 11. Build/version rule
- app version = shared release line
- build number = active PR number during pre-v1 work
- example: PR37 uses version `0.2`, build `37`

### 12. Real-device testing wins
- device behavior overrides simulator assumptions
- user testing feedback overrides “the code looks right”

### 13. Keep fixes local when obvious
- for small obvious code fixes, fix directly instead of punting everything to Copilot

